    "name": "西游-琉璃盏",
    "steam_appid": 1309510,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309510/extras/8799b41144ad1bf2dd6110ec1168c783.avif?t=1755158894\" width=517 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>踏上卷帘大将的传奇之旅，收集琉璃盏碎片，挑战各路强敌，建造属于你的村落，在这个传统与创新交织的西游世界中，成就一段前所未有的冒险。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309510/extras/7fa686a69ff27a120bdc314f103b2d1b.poster.avif?t=1755158894\" width=620 height=318 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309510/extras/7fa686a69ff27a120bdc314f103b2d1b.webm?t=1755158894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309510/extras/7fa686a69ff27a120bdc314f103b2d1b.mp4?t=1755158894\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309510/extras/229be3a2e3a8f6a888d8ba8ad75bd605.avif?t=1755158894\" width=477 height=77 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>卷帘大将因冒犯天庭被贬下界，必须通过收集琉璃盏碎片，逐步恢复力量，面对来自天庭的惩罚。琉璃盏乃龙族供奉天神的灵器，其碎片散落凡间，化为妖族或融入人间。玩家将与各类妖魔鬼怪、人类神仙交锋，收集碎片，并与《西游记》中的经典人物相遇，如美猴王、天蓬元帅、观音菩萨等，重现西游世界的前世今生。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309510/extras/f9815d1acfe26b797a0660a4e8f82172.poster.avif?t=1755158894\" width=620 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309510/extras/f9815d1acfe26b797a0660a4e8f82172.webm?t=1755158894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309510/extras/f9815d1acfe26b797a0660a4e8f82172.mp4?t=1755158894\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309510/extras/4d1011eedc92b0cb1b5391b0cf5c3584.avif?t=1755158894\" width=537 height=77 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏提供了四个章节，包含20多个BOSS战以及上百种武器法宝。每次战斗都是一次全新的挑战，随着剧情推进，玩家将解锁更多的战斗方式与策略。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309510/extras/dfc4b2f259ca70ebee15189dcd398c08.poster.avif?t=1755158894\" width=620 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309510/extras/dfc4b2f259ca70ebee15189dcd398c08.webm?t=1755158894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309510/extras/dfc4b2f259ca70ebee15189dcd398c08.mp4?t=1755158894\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309510/extras/e55ac5841ec101200321161a6318ceb4.avif?t=1755158894\" width=508 height=77 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个章节包含一个主要地图和两个分支地图，地形涵盖山峦、地宫、河面等，地图中的地形模块和怪物组合方式随机变化，体验国风美术的变化。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309510/extras/ef23a334b8e34fe04387e772542d75a4.poster.avif?t=1755158894\" width=620 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309510/extras/ef23a334b8e34fe04387e772542d75a4.webm?t=1755158894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309510/extras/ef23a334b8e34fe04387e772542d75a4.mp4?t=1755158894\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309510/extras/f0878be98a96a9a0cf96d360a78a7ac3.avif?t=1755158894\" width=508 height=77 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个角色拥有上百套动作动画，上千张手绘图片，以及3渲2和Spine立绘动画，呈现出流畅而细致的战斗效果，赋予每个角色独特的战斗风格与视觉表现。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309510/extras/fc0e4c38b74b54892baf172f4339d5a9.poster.avif?t=1755158894\" width=620 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309510/extras/fc0e4c38b74b54892baf172f4339d5a9.webm?t=1755158894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309510/extras/fc0e4c38b74b54892baf172f4339d5a9.mp4?t=1755158894\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309510/extras/90e329704b5cf8128356240da4b8b33c.avif?t=1755158894\" width=527 height=76 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >除了战斗，玩家还能建造并管理自己的村落。游戏提供几十种功能各异的建筑，包括资源生产设施、防御塔、生活区等。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309510/extras/667fce71700e24655eb9a2a6bb4db9bb.poster.avif?t=1755158894\" width=620 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309510/extras/667fce71700e24655eb9a2a6bb4db9bb.webm?t=1755158894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309510/extras/667fce71700e24655eb9a2a6bb4db9bb.mp4?t=1755158894\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
